remarks: A kind of Aristotelian inference.  Namely Felapton or Fesapo . Proposition 59 of [Frege1879] p. 51. _Note:_ in the Bauer-Meenfelberg translation published in van Heijenoort's collection _From Frege to Goedel_, this proof has the ~ frege12 incorrectly referenced.  (Contributed by RP, 24-Dec-2019.) (Proof modification is discouraged.)
statement: frege59b $p |- ( [ x / y ] ph -> ( -. [ x / y ] ps -> -. A. y ( ph -> ps ) ) ) $.
